data.description: Assumable Loan at 3.125% in The Preserve at Tumwater Place Community! This 4-bedroom home offers 2745 sq ft of comfortable living space. Main floor with an inviting open concept design, seamlessly blending living, dining, and kitchen areas, complemented by a versatile den/office. You'll love the granite countertops and a cozy gas fireplace. Step outside to the low-maintenance turf grass backyard, fully fenced for privacy, with a charming pavers patio. Upstairs, discover a primary bedroom complete with an ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. Additionally, the bonus room over the garage offers endless possibilities—it could serve as an extra family room, theater room, or playroom. Located within the sought-after Tumwater School District.
